{"word":"συμπάρειμι","slug":"συμπάρειμι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συμπάρειμι1</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:εἰμί'><el>εἰμί</el></a> <i>sum</i>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to be present also</i> or <i>at the same time</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to stand by, to come to help</i>, <el>τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div> <hr/> <el><b>συμπάρειμι2</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:εἶμι'><el>εἶμι</el></a> <i>ibo</i>\n<p/><i>to go beside also</i> or <i>together</i>, 3 sg. <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a> <el>συμπαρῄει</el>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b><p/>"}]}